Hi there,

You know that feeling when you discover a better way to work, and immediate=
ly want to tell everyone about it?

That's exactly why we're officially launching the *Genspark Genius Program.=
*

A community initiative for people who love Genspark and want to help others=
 learn, connect, and grow with it.

*We're looking for the founding cohort.* People who:

=E2=9C=A8 Know their field well

=F0=9F=9A=80=C2=A0Excited to build community, not just be in one

=F0=9F=A4=9D=C2=A0Get energized by helping others level up

=F0=9F=92=A1=C2=A0Are ready to help shape this from day one

As a Genspark Genius, you can host a local meetup, run a workshop on AI-nat=
ive productivity for your industry, create tutorials, or just start convers=
ations that help people see what's possible.

You'll get support from the Genspark team, early access to what we're build=
ing, and a community of people just as excited about the future of work as =
you are.

This is a chance to do more than participate in the community, it=E2=80=99s=
 a chance to help shape it from day one.

*Ready to help shape this?*

=E2=9C=8D=EF=B8=8FApply to the Genspark Genius Program now! ( https://www.g=
